data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.100 set value "Welcome to the sandpit. Most don't leave."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.101 set value "Saw a Patron out east. Gold symbol, Mythical tier. I ran."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.102 set value "The sun hasn't set in my soul for years."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.103 set value "Oh look, another heatstroke victim with a sword."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.104 set value "A Furia tore through the dunes last night. No name. Just teeth."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.105 set value "No water? No problem. Just kidding, it's a massive problem."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.106 set value "The sand whispers things I wish I could unhear."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.107 set value "That Structure Crate in the temple? Still humming. I hate it."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.108 set value "I once tried to ride a husk. It went poorly."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.109 set value "The cacti have better personalities than most travelers."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.110 set value "My Codex says I have zero luck. Codex is honest."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.111 set value "Another hot day in what someone once called paradise."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.112 set value "Saw a pink glow on the horizon. Exquisite Patron. Stayed home."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.113 set value "Even the rabbits have given up here."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.114 set value "Stay out of the temple. The crate bites back."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.115 set value "You smell like the Nether. That's not a compliment."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.116 set value "We don't get rain. We get disappointment."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.117 set value "The Guidestone stopped glowing. Even it wants to leave."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.118 set value "The desert gives nothing for free. Not even shade."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.119 set value "Another stranger with big dreams and no water supply."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.120 set value "I traded my last emerald for a saddle. Regret tastes dry."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.121 set value "A Dream Surge hit last week. Sky went violet. Lost my chickens."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.122 set value "The stars here are too close for comfort."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.123 set value "We don't dig for treasure. We dig for survival."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.124 set value "Someone found Mjolnir in a ruin south of here. Sure they did."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.125 set value "Heard your stomach growl. That's adorable."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.126 set value "This place builds character. Mostly broken character."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.127 set value "The oasis is a myth. Just like a decent Dream Rate."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.128 set value "Sand in your boots? You'll get used to it. Or you won't."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.129 set value "We measure time by how many husks we've outlived."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.130 set value "A Greater Furia walked past the village. Dark red star. Nobody moved."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.131 set value "Is that a potion or just colored sadness in a bottle?"
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.132 set value "You brought a bed? You poor, naive soul."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.133 set value "The Bartender in the next town over waters down everything."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.134 set value "Sleep here if you enjoy waking up to skeleton arrows."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.135 set value "The sun doesn't rise here. It attacks."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.136 set value "An Uncommon Patron guards the eastern ruins. Blue glow, bad attitude."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.137 set value "Don't follow the rabbits. I mean it."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.138 set value "The cactus told me your future. It was bleak."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.139 set value "I checked the Companion Catalogue. Even pets avoid this biome."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.140 set value "Try not to die. It messes with the vibe around here."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.141 set value "You breathe too loud. Sand punishes that."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.142 set value "Ever eaten dry bread for forty days straight? I have."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.143 set value "Saw the Stormcaller pulse in a traveler's pack. Felt the air change."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.144 set value "Our pets are sand mites. The Catalogue won't list them."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.145 set value "We used to have a librarian. Then the sandstorm took him."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.146 set value "An Expeditionist came through. Said the crates reset faster for her."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.147 set value "Sunburns are our natural armor out here."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.148 set value "You mine diamonds. I mine reasons to keep going."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.149 set value "The Advantage Tree? I'd settle for a regular tree."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.150 set value "Seen any water lately? Me neither."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.151 set value "Don't dig under the well. Something hums down there."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.152 set value "A wandering trader sold me a plushie. Only good day this year."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.153 set value "You're from the forest? Trees sound exhausting."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.154 set value "Some say the temple has traps. Others never said anything again."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.155 set value "Touch my composter and we're enemies for life."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.156 set value "We measure value in cactus flesh and broken dreams."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.157 set value "A Minor Furia spawned by the well. Gray star. Still annoying."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.158 set value "Llamas won't survive here. Just like optimism."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.159 set value "No one cries in the desert. It's too dry for tears."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.160 set value "The Ruin Watch glowed when I walked past the temple. Creepy thing."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.161 set value "Ever tried fishing in sand? Don't bother."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.162 set value "The Harmonize blessings don't stack well with despair."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.163 set value "You look thirsty. You also look lost."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.164 set value "We don't farm for food. We farm to prove a point."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.165 set value "A Rare Patron with the aqua symbol stalks the canyon. Avoid it."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.166 set value "You brought redstone to a desert. Adorable."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.167 set value "Even my shadow abandoned me at noon."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.168 set value "I once had a dream. It dried up like everything else."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.169 set value "The desert doesn't hate you. It just doesn't notice you."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.170 set value "Heard the Heartstone resonates near lava. Perfect for this oven."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.171 set value "Don't sleep too close to the dunes. They shift at night."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.172 set value "You're lucky I'm feeling generous. And dehydrated."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.173 set value "Everything here bites. Including the wind and the silence."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.174 set value "We named the husks. It helps when you scream at them."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.175 set value "The Hunter profession sounds nice until you hunt in this heat."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.176 set value "Every noise after dark is probably your last warning."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.177 set value "The sandstone remembers things the rest of us buried."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.178 set value "I don't fear the dark. I fear what the sand hides in it."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.179 set value "Our golem's cranky. Like me, but taller."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.180 set value "An Ornate Patron with the purple glow guards a ruin. ✲ on its brow."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.181 set value "The temple? Yeah, it has a habit of exploding."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.182 set value "Trading during a raid? That's a whole new kind of stress."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.183 set value "The Artificer two towns over says she can fix anything. Except heat."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.184 set value "Let me guess. You got lost following your Guidestone."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.185 set value "Another map. Another waste of perfectly good paper."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.186 set value "If you find bones in rows, don't ask questions."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.187 set value "Our cats don't meow. They judge silently."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.188 set value "Every villager here owns a shovel and carries trauma."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.189 set value "The Miner profession is popular here. Anywhere underground is cooler."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.190 set value "Your boots are full of sand. Welcome to normal."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.191 set value "Mob Head dropped from a husk once. Put it on a pike as a warning."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.192 set value "We season our food with crushed hopes and cactus salt."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.193 set value "Sand is coarse, irritating, and it gets absolutely everywhere."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.194 set value "Our children play with gravel. Builds resilience."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.195 set value "The Pebble of Dreams sounds useless. I want it desperately."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.196 set value "Build from sandstone. Watch it crumble. Repeat."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.197 set value "Furnaces run all day. The desert is one big furnace anyway."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.198 set value "The savanna villagers complain about heat. Amateurs."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.199 set value "You still here? That's either brave or foolish."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.200 set value "A Dream Surge turned the sky violet. Beautiful. Terrifying."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.201 set value "The wind sometimes carries a melody. Then it stops."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.202 set value "Race a rabbit? They're fast. And they don't share their water."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.203 set value "We may be dry, but at least we're consistently miserable."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.204 set value "The Earthshaker was found in a desert vault. Figures."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.205 set value "The Tomb in the canyon seals things that shouldn't be opened."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.206 set value "I once built a boat in the sand. Still my proudest moment."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.207 set value "Sunshine isn't a mood here. It's a threat."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.208 set value "The golem tripped over a dead bush. Only fun we've had."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.209 set value "Watching husks walk into cacti is free entertainment."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.210 set value "The Weapon Mastery system assumes you survive long enough to learn."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.211 set value "Sometimes I just lie in the sand. Call it meditation."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.212 set value "Who needs oceans when you have endless suffering and dunes?"
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.213 set value "A Nymph came through once. Said the desert lacks spirit. Rude."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.214 set value "Desert life is dry. So is my sense of humor."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.215 set value "The Blaze Core artifact? Born for this climate, honestly."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.216 set value "I saw a mirage. It was me, but happier."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.217 set value "I've got a cactus farm and an attitude problem."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.218 set value "Windrunner boots would change everything. I'd run somewhere cooler."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.219 set value "Sun protection is both fashion and survival strategy."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.220 set value "Water's rare. Sarcasm? Unlimited supply."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.221 set value "The wandering trader had miniblocks. Bought a tiny cactus. Ironic."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.222 set value "Have you hugged a cactus? You shouldn't. But I have."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.223 set value "My crops grow slow but they grow mean."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.224 set value "A Common Patron. Gray glow. Even the weakest ones terrify me."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.225 set value "Husks don't bite if you wink first. Just kidding. They bite."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.226 set value "I've made peace with the sun. It hasn't made peace with me."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.227 set value "We throw sandballs for fun. Duck fast or get buried."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.228 set value "The Beekeeper moved away. Said nothing blooms here. Correct."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.229 set value "The desert is tough. And I'm what's left of tough."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.230 set value "The Kemetian Sword was forged in sands like these. I believe it."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.231 set value "Ever raced a tumbleweed? I lost. Twice."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.232 set value "Structure Crates reset eventually. Patience or madness. Same thing."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.233 set value "We plant hope deep and careful. It still dies."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.234 set value "I saw a baby husk do a little dance. Terrifying. Also cute."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.235 set value "Stars tell stories here. Mostly sad ones."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.236 set value "Sunset tea is just hot water with pretense."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.237 set value "The Acacia Ballista sounds like it belongs out here."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.238 set value "Ever met a desert poet? You're looking at one."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.239 set value "I make sand soup. It's terrible. Want some?"
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.240 set value "A single water drop is worth more than your emerald pile."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.241 set value "Silence is the desert's only gift. Take it."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.242 set value "Heat burns away all lies. And most of your skin."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.243 set value "The Wise Wanderer passed through. Said something deep. I forgot."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.244 set value "Stillness is strength. Also heatstroke. Hard to tell."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.245 set value "The desert does not rush. Neither does death out here."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.246 set value "Your Dream Rate is probably better than mine. Everything is."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.247 set value "Endure long enough and you become part of the sand."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.248 set value "The Kemetian Hoe was made for soil that doesn't exist here."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.249 set value "What thrives here has learned to bend. Or snap quietly."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.250 set value "Hunger sharpens the mind more than any sword."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.251 set value "Kindness evaporates here. Just like everything else."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.252 set value "Each footstep writes a story the wind immediately erases."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.253 set value "Dragon Boots in a desert. Imagine the blisters."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.254 set value "Doubt dries faster than water out here."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.255 set value "The desert sees you coming long before you see it."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.256 set value "Even the sun has to rest. I never get to."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.257 set value "Whoever plants in sand either believes in miracles or is desperate."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.258 set value "A Retired Adventurer settled here. Lasted two weeks."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.259 set value "The desert forgets the weak. Sometimes the strong too."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.260 set value "That sand pile wasn't there yesterday. It's watching you."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.261 set value "We lost a traveler in the temple. Still hear the echo."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.262 set value "The husks come early when the moon goes full."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.263 set value "The Zookeeper visited. Said our animals look depressed. Obviously."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.264 set value "Don't trust shadows that move on their own."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.265 set value "Our well is deep enough to hold every regret I've had."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.266 set value "A Furia with the standard mark aimlessly wanders the canyon."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.267 set value "The wind howled last night. It knew my name."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.268 set value "My neighbor vanished overnight. His bed is still warm."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.269 set value "When stars blink out of order, I go inside."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.270 set value "I swear the dunes breathe when nobody's looking."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.271 set value "The ✣ symbol on that Patron's forehead still haunts me."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.272 set value "If the cactus flowers out of season, something is wrong."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.273 set value "No one survives three sandstorms in a row. Except me. Barely."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.274 set value "The temple door moans when the crate inside refreshes."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.275 set value "The sky's too quiet tonight. That's never good."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.276 set value "You hear that heartbeat under the sand? That's not yours."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.277 set value "A shadow crossed me at noon. It wasn't mine."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.278 set value "Something ancient moves beneath these dunes."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.279 set value "The ☄ symbol means Mythical. If you see it, just pray."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.280 set value "I named all my chickens after failed expeditions."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.281 set value "Yes, I talk to the sun. No, it never talks back."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.282 set value "My favorite food is sand. I'm joking. Mostly."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.283 set value "I made a hat from rabbit hide and regret."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.284 set value "The Guidestone network is the only escape plan I trust."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.285 set value "This robe? Woven from sadness, wool, and sand."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.286 set value "I once proposed to a cactus. We don't discuss it."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.287 set value "During the last Dream Surge the ruins glowed for an hour."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.288 set value "I've trained a rabbit to dance. He's camera shy."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.289 set value "Every sunrise resets my will to care."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.290 set value "That sandstone block judges you. I've seen it."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.291 set value "Someone tried to Harmonize two desert blessings. Got sunstroke twice."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.292 set value "The ✯ Furia mark means Greater. Means run. Means yesterday."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.293 set value "I'm not a villager. I'm a heatstroke hallucination. Maybe."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.294 set value "An artifact pulsed in my dream last night. Woke up sweating."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.295 set value "A sentient tumbleweed would be better company than you."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.296 set value "This sand is haunted. By sand."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.297 set value "I won a staring contest with a blaze once. Desert training."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.298 set value "The phantoms and I have an understanding. Mutual disdain."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.299 set value "I buried my past out back. The sand keeps uncovering it."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.300 set value "Build me shade. Any shade. I am literally begging you."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.301 set value "I need a roof that doesn't leak sand into my bed."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.302 set value "The Kemetian ruins go deeper than anyone admits."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.303 set value "Can you path the way to the well? My feet are just scars now."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.304 set value "Lanterns, please. The dark is when husks get creative."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.305 set value "An entire civilization is buried under these sands. I find pottery shards."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.306 set value "Build a trading hall with actual ventilation this time."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.307 set value "Our bell tower got creepered. Build it again, stronger."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.308 set value "The old Kemetian temples had cooling channels carved in stone."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.309 set value "Make me a lookout on that dune. I want to see death coming."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.310 set value "Beneath the desert floor, old magic still resonates in the stone."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.311 set value "Build me a bench. Standing all day in this heat is inhumane."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.312 set value "Dig a cellar. Only place cooler than a grave out here."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.313 set value "The desert remembers a time before sand. Before the drying."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.314 set value "Raise the walls. Husks keep peeking in like tourists."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.315 set value "Patch that hole before the wind turns it into a doorway."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.316 set value "Grow me melons. They're ninety percent water. I need that."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.317 set value "There were gardens here once. Before the sand swallowed them whole."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.318 set value "Build me a sandcastle. A real one. With structural integrity."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.319 set value "A Kemetian altar lies under the eastern dune. I hear it hum."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.320 set value "We need a stable for the horses nobody can afford."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.321 set value "I could use a shack near the mines. Cool air down there."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.322 set value "Some storage would help. Everything I own is full of sand."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.323 set value "The buried city had banners. Faded gold on deep blue. Beautiful."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.324 set value "Build me a reading nook. Underground. With a door that locks."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.325 set value "Signs everywhere. We keep getting lost in our own village."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.326 set value "Build an altar. These sands have spirits older than memory."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.327 set value "A sandstone arch at the entrance. Make it feel like somewhere."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.328 set value "The ancients carved warnings into the temple walls. We can't read them."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.329 set value "A bakery would be nice. The heat does half the work already."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.330 set value "A marketplace with shade. Shade is the only currency that matters."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.331 set value "Roof the well. I'm tired of fishing sand out of my water."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.332 set value "Stairs on that dune trail. My knees surrendered weeks ago."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.333 set value "Build me a secret room. Underground. You heard nothing."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.334 set value "The Kemetian builders knew something about wind and stone we've forgotten."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.335 set value "A campfire circle. For the stories we tell to stay sane."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.336 set value "Tunnel to the mines. Above ground is a death sentence."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.337 set value "Build a tower. Tall. I want to see if there's anything green anywhere."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.338 set value "Old carvings depict a weapon that split the dunes. Earthshaker, maybe."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.339 set value "Build an oasis. Even a fake one. For morale."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.340 set value "A map room. So I know exactly where I'm choosing not to go."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.341 set value "We need a gate that intimidates pillagers and impresses nobody."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.342 set value "The sand here is older than anything living. It remembers everything."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.343 set value "Build me a bench with a sunset view. Only pretty thing left."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.344 set value "Flowerpots in the windows. Fake flowers. Real ones die instantly."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.345 set value "A tiny museum for all the junk the sand spits back up."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.346 set value "Bells on every corner. Not for raids. For my nerves."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.347 set value "The buried temples go down seven layers. Nobody's reached the bottom."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.348 set value "Give the well a makeover. Glowstone maybe. Something hopeful."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.desert.349 set value "Build something strange. The desert deserves something stranger than itself."
